name: Welcome Message
message:
Hello,

Welcome to the discuss@lists.tungsten.io group at Tungsten Fabric. Please take a moment to review this message.

To learn more about the discuss@lists.tungsten.io group, please visit https://lists.tungsten.io/g/discuss

To start sending messages to members of this group, simply send email to discuss@lists.tungsten.io

If you do not wish to belong to discuss@lists.tungsten.io, you may unsubscribe by sending an email to discuss+unsubscribe@lists.tungsten.io

To see and modify all of your groups, go to https://lists.tungsten.io


Regards,

The discuss@lists.tungsten.io Moderator
